"```sql\nSELECT a.atom_id\nFROM connected c\nJOIN bond b ON c.bond_id = b.bond_id\nJOIN atom a ON c.atom_id = a.atom_id\nWHERE b.molecule_id = 'TR041' AND b.bond_type = '#';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `atom_id` of atoms that are part of a triple bond in the molecule with `molecule_id` 'TR041'. It joins the `connected`, `bond`, and `atom` tables to find the relevant atoms."